{
  "stem": "24111.8",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I never had any money because everything was joined collectively.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And when the war ended in 1949, I decided to leave and do-- and go on my own.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And to bring you on an example, when I was with the first troops into [?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Beer-Sheva ?] and we liberated-- well, not liberated, but we-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] we fought for [?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Beer-Sheva. ?] And [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Beer-Sheva ?] was suddenly in Jewish hands, and there was no Arab left there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We found a [INAUDIBLE] fortress.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We found beautiful buildings.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We found also shabby Arab shacks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But everything was left like it was-- like the Arabs just fled.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And everything was here for the taking.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we didn't take anything, because we-- we thought that doesn't belong to us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we had still more fighting to do.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "When I came the next time back to [?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Beer-Sheva, ?] that was perhaps months later, all those beautiful buildings were already occupied.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they were occupied by people from Romania, Poland-- by latecomers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I felt-- we felt not-- not people which helped us fight, but people which came afterwards, and they took profit of it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But that was not the main point.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I went to work in Tel Nof.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I went work for an engine overhaul.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And in the-- in the meantime, I got also in contact with the-- with people which from my family survive.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "For example, Otto Perl, which was in the-- in Dachau, later on in-- Isle of Man, came to the United States.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I decided-- and the economic situation in '50, '51 in Israel was not a very good one.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "It was a very hard one, a harsh one.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
